The Spiderwick Chronicles;;63;;81;;PG;;Of the three Grace children, Jared (Freddie Highmore) has always been thought of as the troublemaker. So when strange things happen after his family's move to a relative's dilapidated estate, sister Mallory (Sarah Bolger), twin brother Simon and their mother assume that Jared is behind it all. However, magical creatures roam the grounds, and they all want a special book that Jared has found: a field guide to fantastic creatures, penned by Arthur Spiderwick.;;Fantasy,Drama,Kids & family,Adventure;;Mark Waters;;2008;;Freddie Highmore,Sarah Bolger,Mary-Louise Parker,David Strathairn,Nick Nolte,Joan Plowright,Seth Rogen,Martin Short;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spiderwick_chronicles